data.description: Attention Investors! Seller offering 7K credit with acceptable offer. A mountain bungalow with proven rental history on a large lot.  The main floor features 1 Primary Suite with Tray Ceilings, 1 Full Bath, mini-split to heat and cool, and fireplace. Laundry room located on main level. Beautiful hardwood floors through-out most of the home with vinyl floors in the kitchen. The secondary living quarters with seperate ingress and egress features a full primary suite with access to patio. New mini-split installed. New Electric Water Heater, Well Pump and Couplers. Lastly, there is a 407 Sq Ft Detached workshop for your storage needs. Convenient to downtown Brevard, Asheville Regional Airport, Dupont State Forest, Pisgah National Forest, shopping and dining.
